
'''Marthe Yankurije''' (yavutse 5 Nyakanga 1994) ni [[Rwanda|umunyarwanda]] w'umukinnyi wabigize umwuga mukwiiruka intera ndende . Muri 2018, yatsindinze isiganwa ryaberaga u [[Rwanda]] muri metero 10,000 na Shampiyona izenguruka igihugu . Yatsinze kandi isiganwa rya kimwe cya kabiri cya marato muri 2021 ya [[Kigali]] International Peace Marathon, kandi yitabira mu mikino Olempike mu kiciro cya metero 5000 <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/202107300567.html</ref>.

== Umwuga ==
Yankurije ahatanira mu ikipe ya APR Athletics Club; mbere ya 2016, yarushanwe muri Nyamasheke Athletics Club.  Yatangiye imikino ngororamubiri afite imyaka 17  Yatangiye muri marathon ya [[Kigali]] 2014, arangiza ari uwa gatanu, hanyuma nyuma y'umwaka, yitabira amarushanwa ya Afurika Cross Country 2014, arangiza ari 35.  Yaje ku mwanya wa kane mu gice cya kabiri cya marathon muri [[Kigali]] International Peace Marathon 2017  maze atsinda 20 kilometres (12 mi) muri [[Akarere ka Bugesera|Bugesera]] marathon . <ref name="NTBugesera">https://www.newtimes.co.rw/sports/athletics-apr-runners-dominate-bugesera-20km-race</ref> Yankurije yatsindiye metero 10,000 muri Shampiyona yo gusiganwa y'igihugu y'u [[Rwanda]] 2018. <ref>http://www.africathle.com/2018/07/01/rwanda-championship-kigali-1072018/</ref> Muri uwo mwaka, yatsindiye irushanwa ry’igihugu cy’u [[Rwanda]] mu kuzenguruka igihugu <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/sports/hitimana-yankurije-are-national-cross-country-champions</ref> maze aza ku mwanya wa gatatu mu gice cya kabiri cya marathon muri Kigali International Peace Marathon 2018, <ref>https://www.daijiworld.com/news/newsDisplay?newsID=510371</ref> na Dar Marathon muri [[Tanzaniya]]. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/sports/raf-hails-duo-after-dar-marathon-heroics</ref>

Muri 2019, yaje ku mwanya wa kabiri muri Kigali International Peace Marathon , <ref>[https://eng.inyarwanda.com/inkuru/90396/rwandan-marthe-yankurije-wins-second-medal-in-kigali-international-peace-marathon-90396.html#! https://eng.inyarwanda.com/inkuru/90396/rwandan-marthe-yankurije-wins-second-medal-in-kigali-international-peace-marathon-90396.html#!]</ref> maze atsinda 20 kilometres (12 mi) ibyabaye muri [[Akarere ka Bugesera|Bugesera]] na none abisubiramo. <ref name="NTBugesera" /> Muri uwo mwaka, yitabiriye isiganwa rya metero 10,000 mu mikino nyafurika ya 2019 ; yari umwe mu bakinnyi babiri gusa bo mu [[Rwanda]] mu irushanwa.  Muri 2020, yatsinze [[Butare|Huye]] Half Marathon mugihe cya 1:15:15. <ref>http://imvahonshya.co.rw/muhitira-na-yankurije-ni-bo-begukanye-huye-half-marathon-2020/</ref> Yarangije kandi umwanya wa gatatu mu isiganwa rya Trier rya 5 kilometres (3.1 mi) . <ref>https://www.runnersworld.de/news-fotos/silvesterlauf-trier-2020/</ref>

Muri Gicurasi 2021, yitabiriye irushanwa ryo gusiganwa ku maguru muri [[Zambiya]] ryabereye i Lusaka, imikino yo gushaka itike yo kuzitabira imikino Olempike ya 2020 . <ref>https://africafootunited.com/jo-tokyo-2020-tqo-les-rwandaises-marthe-yankurije-et-honorine-iribagiza-en-zambie-pour-une-ultime-chance-de-qualification/</ref> Muri kamena, yatsindinze  igice cya marathon muri Kigali International Peace Marathon. Kubera iyo mpamvu, yahawe ikarita yo mu [[Rwanda]] yo kwitabira imikino Olempike ya 2020. <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/sports/martha-yankurije-turns-focus-olympic-games</ref> Yarushanwe muri metero 5000 ; <ref>https://newtimes.co.rw/sports/tokyo-2020-games-are-rwandan-athletes-ready</ref> yarangije umwanya wa 17  <ref>https://olympics.com/tokyo-2020/olympic-games/en/results/athletics/result-women-s-5000m-rnd1-000200-.htm</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yankurije yavutse muri Nyakanga 1994.  Akomoka mu [[Akarere ka Nyamasheke|Karere ka Nyamasheke]], mu [[Rwanda]]. <ref name="NT19" /> Kw'ishure, yakinaga [[Umupira w’amaguru|umupira w'amaguru]] hamwe na [[Umupira w’intoke|handball]] . <ref name="NT19" /> Yavuye mu ishuri kare, mu mwaka wa kane w'amashuri yisumbuye muri 2012. <ref name="NT19" />

